<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>Great location!! Modest accomodations, but worth the view!! My son and I stayed at this hotel and we had a great time. Location is very important to us and we could not have picked a better hotel for that. Husa Internacional is located directly on Las Ramblas. You walk out of the hotel and you are in the middle of everything! Our flight arrived fairly early in the day and the hotel did not make us wait until the normal check-in time. We requested a balcony room and got it.....overlooking the Ramblas. If you are expecting a luxurious 4-star hotel then this is not the hotel for you. The acccomodations are modest but clean. We did not have unrealistic expectations. Plus, how much time do you spend in your hotel room when in Barcelona???? If we ever travel back to Barcelona, we will definately stay at the Husa Internacional Hotel again, they have all the others beat with location! 
